H(j) = \frac{1}{1} + \frac{1}{2} + \frac{1}{3} + \dots + \frac{1}{j}
H(16) > 3.38
\frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{4} = \frac{7}{12}, \frac{1}{4} + \frac{1}{5} + \frac{1}{7} = \frac{319}{420}  
